<%- include('partials/header') -%>
<main class="container text-tertiary d-flex justify-content-center py-3">
  <div>
    <h1 class="py-3 text-center">Safety and Security</h1>
    <section id="meeting-safety">
      <h2>Meeting Safety</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Plan Your Meeting Publicly</strong></li>
        <p>
          Always meet in a well-populated area with plenty of people around.
        </p>
        <li><strong>Inform Someone</strong></li>
        <p>
          Let a friend or family member know your plans, including where you're
          going, who you're meeting, and when you expect to return.
        </p>
        <li><strong>Use Your Own Transport</strong></li>
        <p>
          Arrange your own transportation to and from the meeting location.
          Avoid accepting rides from people you don't know well.
        </p>
        <li><strong>Trust Your Instincts</strong></li>
        <p>
          If something feels off or uncomfortable, trust your instincts and
          leave the situation.
        </p>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="online-interaction">
      <h2>Online Interaction Safety</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Protect Your Personal Information</strong></li>
        <p>
          Avoid sharing sensitive information such as your home address, phone
          number, or financial details with strangers.
        </p>
        <li><strong>Be Cautious with Personal Details</strong></li>
        <p>
          Share only necessary information and avoid oversharing personal
          details until you’re comfortable.
        </p>
        <li><strong>Verify Profiles</strong></li>
        <p>
          If you’re uncertain about someone, try to verify their profile
          information through additional means, such as mutual connections.
        </p>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="reporting-blocking">
      <h2>Reporting and Blocking</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Report Suspicious Behavior</strong></li>
        <p>
          Report any suspicious or inappropriate behavior through the app.
          Ensure reports are reviewed promptly and appropriate actions are
          taken.
        </p>
        <li><strong>Block Unwanted Contacts</strong></li>
        <p>
          Use the block feature to remove users who make you feel uncomfortable
          or behave inappropriately.
        </p>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="emergency-contacts">
      <h2>Emergency Contacts</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Emergency Help</strong></li>
        <p>
          Contact local emergency services if needed. Have emergency contact
          numbers readily available.
        </p>
        <li><strong>App Support</strong></li>
        <p>
          Reach out to our support team if you need assistance or encounter any
          issues.
        </p>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="safety-tips">
      <h2>Safety Tips for Specific Situations</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>First Meetings</strong></li>
        <p>
          Always meet in public places during daylight hours. Choose locations
          that are familiar and well-lit.
        </p>
        <li><strong>Group Meetings</strong></li>
        <p>
          If meeting a group of people, ensure you’re aware of the group
          dynamics and have mutual connections if possible.
        </p>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="encouraging-safe-practices">
      <h2>Encouraging Safe Practices</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Be Honest and Respectful</strong></li>
        <p>
          Communicate respectfully and honestly with others to build a
          trustworthy environment.
        </p>
        <li><strong>Follow Community Guidelines</strong></li>
        <p>
          Adhere to the app’s community guidelines to foster a safe and
          respectful community.
        </p>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</main>
<%- include('partials/footer') -%>